# Client Components

This document describes the main components used in the React client application.

---

## UI Primitives (`src/components/ui/`)

These are shadcn/ui components - pre-built, accessible primitives. Do not modify directly.

### Available Primitives

| Component        | Description                          |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `button`         | Clickable button with variants       |
| `input`          | Text input field                     |
| `label`          | Form label                           |
| `card`           | Container with header/content/footer |
| `select`         | Dropdown selection                   |
| `dialog`         | Modal dialog                         |
| `form`           | Form wrapper with validation         |
| `popover`        | Floating content panel               |
| `calendar`       | Date picker calendar                 |
| `tooltip`        | Hover tooltip                        |
| `dropdown-menu`  | Dropdown menu with items             |
| `avatar`         | User avatar display                  |
| `table`          | Data table                           |
| `badge`          | Status/label badge                   |
| `skeleton`       | Loading placeholder                  |
| `separator`      | Visual divider                       |
| `scroll-area`    | Custom scrollable area               |
| `sheet`          | Slide-out panel                      |
| `textarea`       | Multi-line text input                |
| `tabs`           | Tabbed interface                     |
| `progress`       | Progress indicator                   |
| `checkbox`       | Checkbox input                       |
| `switch`         | Toggle switch                        |
| `accordion`      | Collapsible sections                 |
| `alert-dialog`   | Confirmation dialog                  |
| `sonner`         | Toast notifications                  |
| `chart`          | Data visualization                   |
| `breadcrumb`     | Navigation breadcrumbs               |
| `sidebar`        | Sidebar layout primitive             |
| `collapsible`    | Collapsible content                  |

---

## Feature Components

### Sidebar (`src/components/Sidebar/`)

Application navigation sidebar with responsive behavior.

**Files:**

- `Sidebar.tsx` - Main sidebar container
- `SidebarNavigation.tsx` - Navigation menu items
- `SidebarHeader.tsx` - Logo and branding
- `SidebarFooter.tsx` - User info and logout
- `MobileMenuButton.tsx` - Hamburger menu for mobile
- `MobileSidebarOverlay.tsx` - Backdrop overlay for mobile
- `SidebarCloseButton.tsx` - Close button for mobile sidebar

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { Sidebar } from '@/components/Sidebar';

const Layout = () => (
  <div className="flex">
    <Sidebar />
    <main className="flex-1">{/* Page content */}</main>
  </div>
);
```

**Context:**

The Sidebar uses `SidebarContext` for state management:

```tsx
import { useSidebar } from '@/context/SidebarContext';

const Component = () => {
  const { isOpen, toggle, close } = useSidebar();
  // ...
};
```

---

### MonthPicker (`src/components/MonthPicker/`)

Month and year selection component for filtering transactions.

**Files:**

- `MonthPicker.tsx` - Main component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { MonthPicker } from '@/components/MonthPicker';

const FilterBar = () => (
  <MonthPicker value={selectedMonth} onChange={setSelectedMonth} />
);
```

---

### GlobalLayout (`src/components/GlobalLayout/`)

Root layout wrapper for the entire application.

**Files:**

- `GlobalLayout.tsx` - Main layout component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { GlobalLayout } from '@/components/GlobalLayout';

const App = () => (
  <GlobalLayout>
    <RouterOutlet />
  </GlobalLayout>
);
```

---

### AuthenticatedLayout (`src/components/AuthenticatedLayout/`)

Layout wrapper for authenticated pages, includes sidebar.

**Files:**

- `AuthenticatedLayout.tsx` - Main layout component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { AuthenticatedLayout } from '@/components/AuthenticatedLayout';

const ProtectedPage = () => (
  <AuthenticatedLayout>
    <Dashboard />
  </AuthenticatedLayout>
);
```

---

### AddCategory (`src/components/AddCategory/`)

Form component for creating new budget categories.

**Files:**

- `AddCategory.tsx` - Main form component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { AddCategory } from '@/components/AddCategory';

const CategoriesPage = () => (
  <div>
    <AddCategory onSuccess={refetchCategories} />
    {/* Category list */}
  </div>
);
```

---

### CategoryCard (`src/components/CategoryCard/`)

Display card for a single budget category.

**Files:**

- `CategoryCard.tsx` - Main card component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { CategoryCard } from '@/components/CategoryCard';

const CategoriesList = ({ categories }) => (
  <div className="grid gap-4">
    {categories.map((category) => (
      <CategoryCard key={category.id} category={category} />
    ))}
  </div>
);
```

---

### TransactionForm (`src/components/TransactionForm/`)

Form for creating and editing transactions.

**Files:**

- `TransactionForm.tsx` - Main form component

**Usage:**

```tsx
import { TransactionForm } from '@/components/TransactionForm';

const AddTransaction = () => (
  <TransactionForm onSubmit={handleSubmit} onCancel={handleCancel} />
);
```

---

### TransactionsList (`src/components/TransactionsList/`)

List display for transactions with filtering and sorting.

**Files:**

- `TransactionsList.tsx` - Main list component

**Usage:**

```tsx
